name: SW Basket 15X12X4 Sloping
description:
Multi Wire Baskets

The cross on these baskets are spaced 7/8" apart so you can display even small items.

Baskets available in white, black, silver or other colors in quantity by special order.

Slatwall baskets are made especially with a long wire to hook into the slot in slatwall. This style of insert spreads the weight in the basket over more of the slot.

All baskets are 7ga. frames and 12ga mesh (unless otherwise listed).
